reviews.review_text: I had a great experience at this McDonald s! The place was spotless, and the staff was friendly and efficient. My meal was delicious and served promptly. Keep up the excellent work, team

Great experience consistently. I was very happy for my hot hash brown, breakfast sandwich and coffee. It was still warm by the time I reached my office in the morning. Drive through was fast and efficient, staff are friendly and polite.

Exceptional service and clean modern interior. I rarely go to McDonalds but I was very impressed with it. They treated my daughter like the princess she is with a crown, crayons and coloring sheets. Employees had a smile and provided service which is rare these days. Good job.
Fast & Friendly staff! Really liked that they used my name and not just my takeout/ pick-up number. Best mcdonalds in the neighborhood! Fries are always hot and salty!!

I head to this location after 12am-3am when I m drunk (my sober gf driving).you ll often see review of  drive through is slow blah blah blah etc  some people don t understand they have a system reboot which results in the delay but that s besides the point. Everytime I come by at such a late hour and always asking for a picky order ie  made fresh please  I have been welcomed with politeness and gratitude for my order. Some people are always polite and nice even working nights shift (beats me, I ve done it and I m a monster during those hours).nonetheless to my surprise, not only was the male who was getting off at 3am was super polite with my order and payment but as I rolled to the last window to pick up my order (you can tell this lady was tired) she was polite, gracious and  patient as I check the bag for the sauces to my delicious nuggets that were made fresh (I know this cause while we were digging through the order it was hot af [she told us  don t burn your hands ]) she didn t make a fuss but told us have a good night after. They all deserve a raise and i send my utmost gratitude for their work (hope they see this) and attitude during the graveyard shift. Thanks guys, I made sure to drop by this one while I drove by other McDonald s on the way home. To the owner, they deserve a raise if not, at least a gift card for their consistent service. I devoured my freshly made cheeseburger (delicious btw) but thought I d post something to legitimize my review. :)

May 24th at around 11:35pm, we made a very customized mobile order and not only was our order made beautifully, the service went above and beyond. Thank you for making our order amazing and your hard work!!!

I did take out so atmosphere didnt apply. The lady working was so nice, it was so fast-the fries were fresh as could be. I was so happy as previously another lady worked there and she was rude & grouchy. The kind of clerk that you say thanks and she doesnt respond - she acts like I should beg, and plead and thank her and she sneers and says nothing..its pretty brutal. But ....I digress the lady 3 nights ago was a total 180, so kind, polite and what a big awesome difference. Thanks to her Ill be back.
Drive thru today (Sunday) and there was no line up.. around 3pm. The service was quick and they got the orders right. Thank you!
Very warm and friendly crew. This location now dining open everyday from 6:am to 2:am not PM so you can come in and dine even until 2:am and Drive Thru 24 hours
Offering very good deals on their App. Big Mac for CAD2 plus taxes only.

Little known fact bill gates owns something like 8% of the McDonalds stock. He talks about using food as a vessel for his medicines and vaccines. How is someone who is so invested in health be a pillar of obesity and bad health in north America.
Clean, friendly staff, clean benches outside, all around i dont give 5 stars . . .maybe today is exceptional. Thank you Sharon for making McDonalds that much more enjoyable! You are so adorable!!
Great experience!!! thank you...

I miss the old McDs from the 1990s the new one doesnt look as neat. Food was hot thats what counts! I had a 10 piece of chicky nuggies with fries   and a ice-t Parking: Big pick-up trucks might have trouble parking here if its really busy
Its a nice place, and have nice customer service!
I had a problem with my app and the servers here were so nice and helpful! Gursharn the area leader went more than an extra mile to help me. She delivered Great Service! Thank you Gursharn! Good job!

I dont usually go to drive thru at  Mcdonalds, but yesterday was an exception as my daughter wanted a treat. So we went through drive thru and ordered at the initial window, which I thought I was done ordering until my daughter wanted french fries. At the paying window, the employee wasnt bothered that I added additional food to my order and she was patient and kind and made me feel like I was not imposing on her line up of cars behind me. She seemed to have everything under control without being dismissive or rude. She just had a really good and positive attitude.

I came here to pick up my online order at the midnight, but somehow the payment cant got through. I tried to reorder, but after 20mins, it still didnt work. Cuz I didnt bring my wallet, I couldnt buy foods directly from the store. The manager or the supervisor of the store just gave me a burger and small fries for free. Thanks to her, I have something to eat. Thanks!
They are open 24 hours. They serve ice cream late. The staff are really friendly. The service is fast. They have never gotten my order wrong. I always get hot fries. And I appreciate all of that.

This is my favourite McDonalds to go to, its always so fast an efficient. Some of the people at the drive through window I recognize from being there for quite a while and they have worked up to positions with more responsibility which is great. Im usually a mobile app ordering person but its very streamlined to get through the drivethrough pickup, so thanks for that!
The woman leading everyone in the kitchen made operations efficient, got food in timely manner and it tasted great.
Night Drive through window lady made me laugh... nice when staff has a great spirit and a sense of humor ( appropriate of course )..makes the experience memorable. Superb performance

As you drive up to the drive-thru the ordering system has an automated message just simply wait for the automated message to finish playing through and allow them to greet you to take your order. five stars.
Geeta was very polite and had a positive welcoming attitude! We definitely recommend visiting this McDonald s for quality service
The manager was very nice and took my last minute order since our camper wouldnt fit thru the drive-thru. Thank you since it was -15 on that night!!
I get coffee from this Dons like everyday. It s essential to my life, and the workers here are always chill. The place is always clean and there s usually some old people chillin at the tables.
